The "m_Lightmapping" value of 4 corresponds to Baked Lighting in Unity. Here is the fixed code snippet:

```
Light:
m_Lightmapping: 2
```

Please note that this change will not affect the real-time lighting of your static objects. The scene will use baked and real-time lighting as per your settings, but the difference may not be noticeable unless your static objects have complex materials or textures.
